history.content: Come out to support the Tech+ Social Impact team to meet Technical Program Manager at Google and Harvard alum Gracie Elqura and learn about the innovative ways technology can be used to improve education. From course/curriculum development to learning theory to developing creative technologies for learning, Gracie has done it all. It’s next Saturday Nov. 17th 11AM-12:30PM at the HP auditorium (Soda 306). Also, free Sliver and drinks provided! RSVP at the link: https://www.facebook.com/events/740787012950825/
history.subject: Tech+ Social Impact Talk with Gracie Elqura
